There was a nod from CONVOY, &quot;I know your goal and I have heard your
reason why, and perhaps yet you will have your chance to make good on
it. But in order to achieve it you must still be free, not locked up
in solitary confinement waiting on the torturous pleasure of
Saberback.&quot;

&quot;Yeah, plus I am sure the mech will be chasin&#39; us for sure anways.&quot;
NIGHT VIPER said as he disappeared back into the hole.

The hole itself was just wide enough for BIG CONVOY and TUSCON to fit
in, one by one, in robot mode, their shoulders perhaps a foot or less
from scraping each side.

The hole looked to go into a tunnel that had been meticulously carved
out by someone, and then ladder steps cut into it to allow for
movement. It was lit by small lamps near the top of the hole, the hole
itself leading down into darkness.

Just before leaving BIG CONVOY took a device and used it to scan
TUSCOn and then laid it in the recharging chamber that TUSCON would
have used and then placed one in his own. After a moment a hologram of
each of them flickered into place.

&quot;There that should hold them for a while.&quot; CONVOY said as he motioned
for TUSCON to get in the hole. &quot;It&#39;s time to move. It will be chamber
check time in a few micro-klicks (Minutes)&quot;

